Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,博亚卡  哥伦比亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,猎人 前情提要\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Previously on Hunters...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那则音频信息中说会发生流血事件 现在的确发生了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}That audio message said blood would be spilt, and it has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那个带走艾比的混球\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}The bastard who took Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我们找到他 就能找到你妻子\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We find out where he is, we find your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我老婆怎么会是你们中的一员呢\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}My wife is not one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,现在想看艾比吗 来吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You wanna see Abby now? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在仓库里的尸体上采集了一些证物\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We got some forensics off the body in the warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,发现受害者体内有海洛因\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Turns out there was heroin in the victim's system.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是艾比\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's not Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们无处不在 我们所向披靡\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We're everywhere, and you can't stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是斯拉维奇的妻子\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Slavich's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我把那女人撕成碎片\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I tore that woman to shreds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就像野兽一样 我还喜欢那种感觉\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}like an animal... and I liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,里根特工就像眼镜蛇一样蜕皮\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Agent Regan is shedding like a freakin' cobra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,斯拉维奇跟我说的最后一句话就是我们组里有内鬼\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Slavich's last words to me were about Hunters being inside the ETU.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,里根很困惑\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Regan's confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他觉得她是他们中的一员\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}He think she's one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她最好小心\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}She better watch herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,塞克莱顿市 西弗吉尼亚州 1997
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 怎么了 艾莉森\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}- Hey! - What is it, Allison?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能别玩这个\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Could you play something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你在逗我吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,噪音刺得我头疼\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}The noise hurts my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你这人真奇怪\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You are so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉森\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Allison?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是意外 爸爸\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It was an accident, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 我的天哪  - 对 对不起\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}- Oh, my God. - I'm... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她没事的  - 泰德 发生什么事了吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}- She's okay. - Ted, everything all right out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要帮助 快报警\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We need help! Call 911!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,打电话报警  他们需要帮助\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Call 911! They need some help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在麦卡锡仓库内找到的瘾君子尸体内\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}The junkie body we found in McCarthy's warehouse
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有哥伦比亚·奥尔维多的海洛因\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}had Columbian Olvidos' heroin in her system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,美国缉毒局去年拍到麦卡锡和五胞胎还有奥尔维多在一起的照片\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}DEA got pictures of McCarthy and the Quins with the Olvidos last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对自己面临的事情完全不了解\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}They had no idea who or what they were dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,五胞胎  是我在仓库见到的那些怪胎\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Quins? Those are the freaks I saw at the farmhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对 这是我们起的名字\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}That's what we're calling 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这些照片是在通往\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}This picture was taken on a road
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哥伦比亚丛林深处一制毒窝点的路上拍的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}leading to a drug compound deep in the Columbian jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,猎人和海洛因 还有如穆斯林圣战者般的藏身地点\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Hunters and heroin, and deep like a Mujahidin situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那是筹集资金的最佳方法\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Tried and true method of raising funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,女童子军有饼干 恐怖分子有毒品\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Girl Scouts have cookies, terrorists have dope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,里根 你听明白了吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Regan. You getting all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,猎人在丛林里倒手毒品\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}The Hunters are running drugs in the jungle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我和一个新来的人去找他们\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}and you're sending me a new guy to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 收到  - 算上我\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}- Got it. - Count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,卡罗尔特工有啃药史 布里格斯\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Agent Carroll has history with narcotics, Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是担心他\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's not him I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道认为我需要保护吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You think I need protecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不如问问杰西·斯拉维奇吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Oh, let's ask Jessie Slavich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有里根特工在 你才能坐在这里 闭上你的嘴\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Agent Regan is the only reason you're still here to shoot your mouth off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你和卡罗尔\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You and Carroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我个人认为\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}My two cents...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们要去丛林抓猎人的话 多一个士兵不是坏事\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}if we're going into the jungle to catch Hunters, another soldier couldn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 布里格斯 算你一个\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}All right... Briggs, you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,共同合作 找到他们的大本营 捣毁它\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Work together, find this camp, shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住任何你能找到的猎人或是同伙\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Capture any Hunters or collaborators you may find.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之前用过几个当地人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}There are some local guys we've used before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以相信他们\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You can trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我来处理麦卡锡的善后工作\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I'll handle the McCarthy cleanup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要拿走这些\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I'm taking these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的全家福吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Family pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑啦\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I was kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:03:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别那么严肃\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Lighten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你依然是位已婚男士吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Thought you were still a married man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会在这里处理我的皮肤问题的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I'm not getting down to my skin in here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,关于你的皮肤\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}About your skin thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还要讨论这个\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We're still on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,请便\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还有没有其他方法\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Is there any other way to, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,辨别某人是不是……\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}tell if someone is... whatever you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我有强烈的欲望 生理上的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I get urges, physical urges.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很难控制\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}They're hard to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你说生理是指\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You mean physical like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 没错  还有\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Yes, that. And other stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,冲动\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Impulse control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,饥饿 愤怒\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Hunger, rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她在抱怨自己的感觉吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Is she blaming her feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,接着就得开始抱怨经前综合征了吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Next she'll say it was PMS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,饶了她吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Give her a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,江山易改本性难移\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}A tiger doesn't change its stripes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去的地方 将需要她发挥身上的每一个长处\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Where we're going, were gonna need everything she's got in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,塞克莱顿市 西弗吉尼亚 1997
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉森 你在做什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Allison... what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过那个声音会刺痛你的耳朵\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You said that hurts your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是这样\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Sweetie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你对妮可做的 不过是个意外\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What happened to Nicole... was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No, it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让她停下 所以就推了她\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I wanted her to stop, so I pushed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但你并不想伤害她\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}But you didn't mean to hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你的错\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}This was not your fault.
