Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗  跟直觉走就好了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Okay? Just follow your instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你会没事的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧从窗户出去  现在  马上\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Now out the window. Now. Go, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她说一只怪物带走了她的母亲\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}She says a monster took her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物  什么样的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}A monster? How it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}How it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,再问问她\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Ask her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要弄清楚她到底看到了什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We need to know exactly what she saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是拉莫哈娜\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's La Mojana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当地传说里的人物\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's a local legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一个可以改变外形的女人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}A woman that changes shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,引诱人进丛林 然后吃了他们\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}takes people into the jungle and eats them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,毒枭宣传这个传说以阻止农民进入丛林\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}The cartel encourages it to keep peasants out of the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是莫哈娜吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It was the Mojana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,带走你妈妈的那个人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}That took your Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  拉莫哈娜\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Yes. La Mojana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,拉莫哈娜\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}La Mojana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得把她带回她的营地\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We need to get her back to the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  她就待在这里\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No, no, no... she stays.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,前方险阻未知\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We're walking into a shit storm,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要人手 抓一个是一个\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}and I need every soldier I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她还是个孩子\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}She's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把她带回去\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I'm taking her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你有任务\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You got a job to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们一起\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,弗林说得没错\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Flynn's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  出现了个拉莫哈娜\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Oh... we got La Mojana out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你就突然离不开我咯\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}and suddenly you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,唷 芭比大兵 她是个大姑娘啦\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Yo, G.I. Joe Barbie, she's a big girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我在她那么大的时候 都手撕好几人了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I was slitting throats when I was her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你想拿到之前杰克逊答应的薪水吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You want your payday like Jackson promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,让你最弱的手下带这姑娘回营地\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Send your weakest man to take the girl back to camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不然的话 我们来带\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}otherwise, we take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你就什么也捞不着\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}And you go home empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你做决定吧 头儿\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Choice is yours, jefe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,卡洛斯\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Carlos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,卡洛斯 把这女孩儿带回营地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候告诉他 我们是在打怪物 而不是对抗毒枭\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}When do we tell him we're fighting monsters and not a drug cartel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也不用说\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We don't tell them anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他们也不是怪物\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}And they're not monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是非人类罢了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}They're just not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,阿勒格尼山脉 西弗吉尼亚州 2005
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在读这个的话 说明我已经不在你身边了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}If you're reading this, it means I'm no longer with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在起得靠自己了 你要坚强\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You're on your own now, and you have to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你做什么 我都是你的父亲\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No matter what you do, I am your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的小心肝\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}and you're my little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我会永远爱你\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}And I will always love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这边\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一直向前\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们找到营地了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I think we found our camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看来没人啊\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Looks empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没有看守 什么都没有\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No guards, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,废墟\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Ghost town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,里根\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Regan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我听不到动静\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I don't hear a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从下面过去吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Let's move in from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,安全\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,空无一人  外面的尸体一定是工人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Empty. The bodies outside must be the workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大屠杀  - 安全\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}- A massacre. - Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没有枪伤\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No bullet wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没有枪战的痕迹  只有\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No signs of firefight. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,被分尸的尸体\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Ripped apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是谁这么心狠手辣\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What the hell could have done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,弗林\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Flynn?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你发现了什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,脚印\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来是不久前的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}They look fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.72,0:23:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 这是我的问题\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Shut up, it's my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.88,0:23:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嗯 我们搜索了整个营地\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Hey... yeah, we searched the entire camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.50,0:23:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,无人生还\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}There's no one left here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也没发现什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Nothing more to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不 还不能走\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No, we're not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在返程 还能在天黑前回去\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We go now, we might make it back before dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.96,0:23:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 他们要睡觉了吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Oh, is it past their bedtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Yeah... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们已经完成了任务 把你们带到营地\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}'Cause we did our job... got you to the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我答应杰克逊的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}That's what I told Jackson we'd do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,已经完成了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}and it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的林地吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Is this your jungle?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拿出你该有的样子\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Then act like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不是为缉毒行动来的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You're not here for a drug bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,布里格斯 我们一起守夜吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Briggs... let's set up a watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,轮流守 一直到明天早上\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We'll take shifts till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,马托 你和你的部下\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Mato... you and your men
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可以清理下外面的尸体\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}can clean up the bodies outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.72,0:23:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去搜查制毒室\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We'll search the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在生产海洛因\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}They were producing heroin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.90,0:24:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看这个\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.82,0:24:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这具尸体和外面的不同\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}That body wasn't killed like the ones outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.22,0:24:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口和麦卡锡仓库里的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's the same wounds as the junkie
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,瘾君子一样\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}in McCarthy's warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.90,0:24:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我捣毁过很多制毒窝点\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I've raided dozens of drug labs,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.34,0:24:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,从没见过这样的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I've never seen anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.20,0:24:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,此事另有隐情\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Something else was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.86,0:24:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还是暖的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's still warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.30,0:25:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在破坏证据\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}They were destroying evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.64,0:25:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,和人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}And people.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.50,0:25:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,计划周全 毫无破绽\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No loose ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.40,0:25:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们好像一直先我们一步\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Like they were one step ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.68,0:25:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,斯拉维奇跟我说 我们有内鬼\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Slavich told me they had someone on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.98,0:25:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,内鬼  不可能吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}A mole? That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.46,0:25:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.62,0:25:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是外皮\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Yeah, it's skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.44,0:25:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.56,0:25:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,某种身体组织 不是人类的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's some kind of tissue, not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.84,0:25:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们到底在这儿干嘛\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What the hell were they doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.02,0:25:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,去掉痛苦\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Taking the pain away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.69,0:25:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,芝加哥 伊利诺斯州 2012
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.07,0:26:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还想拿奖赏么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You want a medal?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.67,0:26:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我交班时间快到了  滚边儿\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}My break's almost over. Shoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.00,0:26:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,疯婊子\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Crazy fucking bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.02,0:26:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我会打电话给你的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I'll call you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.72,0:26:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,才怪\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.84,0:26:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.70,0:26:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在干什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What are you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.43,0:26:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,关你屁事 臭傻逼\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}None of your business, dick wad.
