Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.20,0:26:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到的  蠢驴\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You heard me, donut ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.06,0:26:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,面对墙站好\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Up against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.80,0:26:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,放了他\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.86,0:26:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,放了他 不然我开枪了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Let him go, or I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.86,0:27:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,听见什么没  在外面吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Hear anything? Is it out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.62,0:27:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  可能吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I don't know. Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.52,0:27:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,天没亮 什么也干不了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Can't do much till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.46,0:27:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,至少第一个被五马分尸的会是布里格斯\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}At least Briggs will be the first one getting ripped apart.
