Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.90,0:27:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很复杂\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.82,0:27:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Did you two...?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.30,0:27:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 天\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No. No. God, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.32,0:27:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是他的菜\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I'm not his type.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.24,0:27:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 他喜欢独来独往\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Besides, he's kind of a loner,
