Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.48,0:28:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能说我怪他\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Can't say I blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.80,0:28:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过一些人做出极恶之事\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I've seen human beings do some heinous shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.69,0:28:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但我从没见过这样的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}But I've never seen anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.66,0:28:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,来点吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}This helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.60,0:28:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以酒对你的影响不像\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}So alcohol doesn't affect you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.16,0:28:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  但我喜欢喝酒这种活动\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No. No. But I like the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.62,0:28:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,让我觉得自己是正常人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It makes me feel normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.48,0:28:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你相反\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's pretty much the opposite for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.10,0:28:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢它让我觉得自己没那么正常\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I like how it makes me feel not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.20,0:28:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是一直看起来都那么像\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Did you always look... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.27,0:28:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  人类\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What? Human?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.27,0:29:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,自打我记事起就是\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}As far as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.85,0:29:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为自己是呢 直到我父母告诉我不是\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Thought I was, until my parents told me I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.84,0:29:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的妻子 你从没怀疑过\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Your wife... you never suspected?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.88,0:29:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.32,0:29:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能是外星人吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}That she could be from outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.96,0:29:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.64,0:29:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我特么为什么要那么想\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Had no damn reason to think she might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.23,0:29:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但 看着你\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}But, watching you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.42,0:29:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得还真有可能\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I'd say it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.82,0:31:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,米格尔\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Miguel!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.80,0:31:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,米格尔 欧内斯托\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Miguel, Ernesto!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.09,0:31:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,回来  回来\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Come back! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.96,0:31:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好运  我逃命去了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Good luck. I'll back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.28,0:31:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,米格尔  你在哪里\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Miguel! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.06,0:31:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你死定了 你个混蛋\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You're gonna fry, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.33,0:31:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,马托的手下全被杀死了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}This killed all of Mato's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.77,0:31:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么鬼\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.82,0:31:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,它要逃走了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.46,0:31:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.78,0:32:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Whatever it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.14,0:32:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,反正不是人类\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}it wasn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.94,0:32:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手机呢  我要叫后援\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Where's my cell phone? I'm calling in backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.82,0:32:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,如果必要 我真要叫上所有军队\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}The whole God damn army if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.30,0:32:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要找到那东西 然后杀了它\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We will find that thing and go kill it...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.76,0:32:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,能告诉我 这到底是怎么一回事吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Wanna tell me what the hell that was about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.42,0:32:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,保密协议  杰克逊的命令\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Containment protocol. Jackson's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.31,0:32:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他看到太多了  他会说出去的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}He saw too much. He was about to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.84,0:33:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她说得没错  地外反恐行动组的规定\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}She's right. ETU rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.20,0:33:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能让别人知道这些\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We can't let any of this get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.02,0:33:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死他手下的东西还在外游荡\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Whatever killed his men is still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.56,0:33:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须通知杰克逊 走吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We need to notify Jackson, get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.12,0:33:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,里根 如果我没有加入行动组\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Regan, if I hadn't have joined the unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.19,0:33:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你也会把我处置掉吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}would you have... contained me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.27,0:33:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不是人类外表吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Not in human form?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.44,0:33:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那是披着什么皮的怪物\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Well, what form is it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.93,0:33:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I don't know, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.20,0:33:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能确定是一个猎人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}All I know for sure is that it's a Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.18,0:33:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,马托也看见了吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}And Mato saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.70,0:33:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他有没有被\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Has he been...?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.52,0:33:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,已经解决了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's been handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.34,0:33:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你的所谓保密协议 令我们人手紧缺\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Your protocol left us shorthanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.28,0:33:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要额外支援  派空中之眼无人机过来\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We need additional support. Eyes in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.16,0:33:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽力而为\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.40,0:33:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在就需要  等不到明天早上了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We need it now. Can't wait till the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.34,0:33:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白  - 那东西晚上也能行动\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}- Understood. - That thing can hunt at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.69,0:33:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,它有优势\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It has the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.80,0:33:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你能定位目标对象的位置吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You have a location on the target?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.54,0:33:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,它受伤了 而且很害怕\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's injured, scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.34,0:33:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得它会躲到山里去\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I think it'll head to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.64,0:33:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得还是你确定\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You think or you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.50,0:33:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我会这么做\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}That's what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.78,0:33:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就我们对他们语言的了解而言 还算说得过去\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}That makes sense with what we understand about their language.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.33,0:33:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,地势越高\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Higher elevation means more miles
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.38,0:33:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,越能先发制人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}to anticipate potential attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.44,0:33:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们原本一个小时之内就可以派无人机过去\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We could have a drone out there in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.40,0:34:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么状况了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}And then what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.74,0:34:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有个爱荷华州的22岁的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}22-year-old kid from Iowa
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.54,0:34:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,斯诺登狂饭 用游戏机控制器\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}with an Xbox controller and a Snowden complex
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.69,0:34:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,把无人机黑掉了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}gets one of these things in his sights?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.18,0:34:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么解决\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}How do we contain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.48,0:34:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,车到山前必有路\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We'll cross that bridge when we come to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.80,0:34:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我会联系兰利\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I'll reach out to Langley.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.52,0:34:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们真想抓到它 现在就应该出发了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}If we wanna catch this thing, we gotta leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.50,0:34:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ETU曾经抓到过跟你不一样的猎人吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Has ETU ever caught one that doesn't look like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.94,0:34:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从未抓到过任何形态的活口\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We've never captured one alive in any form.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.40,0:34:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们这次最好能抓到一个 对吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Then we better... catch this one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.23,0:34:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,天那么黑 我们怎么找得到它\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}How we gonna find it in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.52,0:34:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有志者事竟成\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You can find anything if you want it badly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.83,0:34:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,库克郡惩教中心 伊利诺斯州 芝加哥市 2012年
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.58,0:35:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉森 你好\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Hello, Allison.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.50,0:35:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫特拉斯·杰克逊\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}My name is Truss Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.60,0:35:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我来自国土安全部\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Homeland Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.80,0:35:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是来伤害你的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I'm not here to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.74,0:35:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看什么看 你个糟老头\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Stop staring, you dirty old freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.26,0:35:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么着 以前没见过女的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What, you never seen a girl before?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.87,0:35:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只是没见过你这样的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.70,0:35:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,几年前  我把你的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I have an... old photograph of you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.10,0:35:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一张老照片录入系统\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}that I put into the system years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.09,0:35:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就怕你万一哪天被警察逮捕\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}just in case you ever got arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.86,0:35:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这张\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}And here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.23,0:35:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,挺可爱\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Cute kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.64,0:35:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是我\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}But that's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.21,0:35:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉森·里根 来自西佛吉尼亚州的塞克莱顿市\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Allison Regan of Circleton, West Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.75,0:35:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,泰德·里根与利安娜·里根的女儿\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Daughter of Ted and Liana Regan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.22,0:36:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没听说过\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Never heard of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.61,0:36:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,16岁时 家里被不明入侵者闯入 而失踪\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Disappeared age 16 after a home invasion by unidentified intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.37,0:36:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定这不是你吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You sure that's not who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.01,0:36:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,行动\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.77,0:36:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,兰利不允许\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Langley said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.30,0:36:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 行动终止  - 为什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}- You have to abort. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.12,0:36:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.93,0:36:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有后援 你们不堪一击\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Without backup, you're vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.61,0:36:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有无人机 你们什么都看不见\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Without a drone, you're blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.78,0:36:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,太危险了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.11,0:36:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,它受伤了  优势在我们这边\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's injured. We have the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.81,0:36:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,它可是猎人的新变体\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}It's a new form of Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.02,0:36:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,行动终止\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Abort.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.08,0:36:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是命令\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.62,0:36:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,信号不好  你要我们汇报吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You're breaking up. You said report?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.86,0:36:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,行动终止  我说终止\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Abort! I said abort.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.73,0:36:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,收到  我们会在完成任务后向您汇报 完毕\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Copy that! We'll complete the mission and report, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.62,0:36:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,卡罗尔\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Carroll!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.05,0:36:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这回要倒大霉了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We're gonna catch shit for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.48,0:37:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,最好物有所值\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Well, we better make it worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.23,0:37:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在树上\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}In the trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.75,0:37:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,布里格斯\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Briggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.59,0:37:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,布里格斯\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Briggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.52,0:37:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真特么见鬼\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.93,0:37:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没事  - 是那些毒贩子设下的陷阱\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}- I'm okay. - A perimeter trap from the drug cartel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.39,0:37:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,用得着你说\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Oh, now you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.44,0:37:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  数到三\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Ready? On three.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.81,0:37:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧  - 1\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}- Go on. - One...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.59,0:37:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,喀嗒声越来越弱了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}The clicks are getting fainter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.93,0:37:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你去追吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}All right, you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.91,0:37:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我来照看布里格斯\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I'll take care of Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.35,0:38:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她会被那个生物撕碎的\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}She could get ripped by whatever that thing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.56,0:38:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能反过来\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Or she tears it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.24,0:38:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,正好两不耽误 双赢\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}What they call a win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.70,0:38:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.97,0:38:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,里根又怎么惹着你了\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}So what's your beef with Regan?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.16,0:38:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不像你那么喜欢人形猎人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Oh, I don't like human Hunters like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.56,0:38:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她真他妈能干\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}She's been pretty damn useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.37,0:38:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是我见过的唯一一个猎人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}She's not the only one I've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.53,0:38:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经与澳洲特种部队在阿富汗执行任务\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I was with Australian Special Forces in Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.64,0:38:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还以为找到了恐怖分子的巢穴\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}We thought we were hitting a terrorist cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.37,0:38:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,结果房间里只有一个人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Turned out to be just one guy in a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.41,0:38:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两人冲进去\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Two of us went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.21,0:39:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,火力大开\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Opened fire, both clips.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.24,0:39:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那人毫发未伤\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.98,0:39:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,然后\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.63,0:39:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,它扑向布兰登\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}it leapt at Brendan
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.18,0:39:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,把他撕成了碎片\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}and it ripped him apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.68,0:39:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不慌不忙 戏弄意味十足\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}But slowly... playfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.11,0:39:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就像猫戏弄老鼠一样\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Like a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.45,0:39:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,整个过程中\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}And the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.85,0:39:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它一直盯着我\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}it kept looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.62,0:39:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那是一场表演\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Like it was a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.05,0:39:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,猎人夺走了你所爱之人\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Hunters took the one you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.86,0:39:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有同样遭遇\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}They did that to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.41,0:39:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能相信她\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You can't trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.17,0:39:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不管外表再怎么纯良\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}And whatever they look like on the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.95,0:39:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它们骨子里还是恶魔\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}they're monsters underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.55,0:40:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利诺斯州 芝加哥市 2012年
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.68,0:40:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你太狠了吧\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You're ruthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.18,0:40:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,世界尽在我的掌控之中\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}World domination cometh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.64,0:40:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你的杀人本能是来自父母的吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You get the killer instinct from your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.21,0:40:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我父母不是早死了么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}My parents are dead, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.16,0:40:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 我们对你 你的父母\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Truth is, we don't know much about anything about...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.13,0:40:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,都了解甚少\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}your parents, about you, about any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.23,0:40:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你狗屁不懂\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}So you don't know shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.70,0:40:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你不了解我\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Not about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.25,0:40:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没人了解我\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}No one does.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.69,0:41:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多年来 你一直留着父亲给你的信\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}You kept his letter from your dad for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.58,0:41:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都需要精神支柱\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Everybody needs someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.72,0:41:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你的父母\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Your parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.68,0:41:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们和你一样\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}they were like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.36,0:41:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.84,0:41:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.44,0:41:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一样\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}They were like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.82,0:41:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是什么\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}And what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.27,0:41:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fnNyala\fs40\shad0\b0}I don't know.

